Adrian Ropes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrian_Ropes 0 Adrian Ropes (8 May 1941 – 11 March 2004) was an Egyptian-born English television actor. He appeared in British television series Emergency – Ward 10, The Human Jungle, The Avengers, Randall and Hopkirk, Budgie and others.
